        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/1"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The natural assets are the animals and also the mountain wind to cure the meat. The social asset relates to the regional brand as a way of cooperation among the producers. Finally, the cured meat is a traditional meal in the country and represents part of the food heritage.   </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


